The '''Los Angeles Times Syndicate''' was a newspaper publishing syndicate that distributed a number of [[comic strip]]s. It was the publisher of the [[Star Wars (comic strip)|''Star Wars'' newspaper comic strips]] that were published in U.S. and Canadian newspapers from [[March 11]], [[1979]] through March 11, [[1984]], alongside the [[Watertown Daily Times]].

